    },
    {
      "text": "BATTLE PINGPONG (バトルピンポン) is a Japanese table tennis video game developed and published by Quest for the Game Boy exclusively in Japan. It was released in Japan on August 31, 1990 and never saw a release in another territory, although the game was going to be published by Sammy in America. The game allows the player to either compete in a tournament or vs. mode against 8 nations.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
